sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { PassengerService } from './../api/services/passenger.service'; import { FormBuilder } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register-passenger', templateUrl: './register-passenger.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register-passenger.component.css'] }) export class RegisterPassengerComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private passengerServices: PassengerService, private fb: FormBuilder) { } form = this.fb.group({ email: [''], firstName: [''], lastName: [''], isFemale: [true] }) ngOnInit(): void { } register() { //ovo metoda je povezana u html sa dugmetom Login console.log("Form Values:", this.form.value) this.passengerServices.registerPassenger(); } }
